						<summary>

						<p>This registers the grant of 50 <hi rend="italic">mattars</hi> of land and a flower garden made by <hi rend="bold">Baṇṭarasa</hi> during the reign of the Chālukya king <hi rend="bold">Vijayāditya-Satyāśraya</hi> to <hi rend="bold">Dharmma-Bhaṭāra</hi> and some land to a temple with the consent of the <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas.</hi> The record is not dated.</p>						

						</summary>
